      <li>Includes a<b> : (colon)</b> at the end</li><br>
      <li>Indentation matters!</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <img src="https://images.code.org/6fe95faab436e5dc247f5443c9907e43-image-1741629976193.png" 
